  • Constructor Details

    • EmedPreEntryDigest

      public EmedPreEntryDigest(Instant prescriptionTime, UUID documentId, @Nullable AuthorDigest documentAuthor, @Nullable AuthorDigest sectionAuthor, UUID entryId, UUID medicationTreatmentId, int sequence, @Nullable String annotationComment, MedicationDosageInstructions dosageInstructions, MedicationProduct product, @Nullable Integer repeatNumber, @Nullable RouteOfAdministrationAmbu routeOfAdministration, Instant prescriptionDocumentValidityStart, @Nullable Instant prescriptionDocumentValidityStop, Instant itemValidityStart, @Nullable Instant itemValidityStop, @Nullable RenewalInterval renewalPeriod, @Nullable EmedReference mtpReference, boolean provisional, boolean substitutionPermitted, @Nullable String treatmentReason, @Nullable String patientMedicationInstructions, @Nullable String fulfilmentInstructions, boolean inReserve, @Nullable String quantityToDispense)
      Constructor.
      Parameters:
      prescriptionTime - The prescription time.
      documentId - The parent document unique ID.
      documentAuthor - The author of the original parent document or null if they're not known.
      sectionAuthor - The author of the original parent section or null if they're not known.
      entryId - The item entry ID.
      medicationTreatmentId - The ID of the medication treatment this item entry belongs to.
      sequence - The sequence of addition.
      annotationComment - The annotation comment or null if it isn't provided.
      dosageInstructions - The dosage instructions.
      product - The medication product.
      repeatNumber - Number of repeats/refills (excluding the initial dispense). It's a non-zero integer if it's limited, it's zero if no repeat/refill is authorized and null if unlimited repeats/refills are authorized.
      routeOfAdministration - The medication route of administration or null if it's not specified.
      prescriptionDocumentValidityStart - The inclusive instant at which the prescription shall start.
      prescriptionDocumentValidityStop - The inclusive instant at which the prescription shall stop or null if it's not bounded.
      itemValidityStart - The inclusive instant after which the first full dispense shall happen.
      itemValidityStop - The inclusive instant before which the first full dispense shall happen or null if it's not bounded.
      renewalPeriod - The renewal period or null if it's not specified.
      mtpReference - The reference to the MTP entry, if any.
      provisional - Whether this prescription item is provisional or not.
      substitutionPermitted - Whether the substitution is permitted (Equivalent) or not (None).
      treatmentReason - The treatment reason or null if it isn't provided.
      patientMedicationInstructions - The patient medication instructions or null if it isn't provided.
      fulfilmentInstructions - The fulfilment instructions or null if it isn't provided.
      inReserve - Whether the treatment is to be taken regularly (false) or only if required (true).
      quantityToDispense - The quantity to dispense or null if it isn't provided.
      Throws:
      InvalidEmedContentException - if the validity periods are invalid.
